title: When you run into this...

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body:
Game started with Thresh taxing monster - haha, just wow...

Then Fiora proceeds to give first. Ekko goes back, meets Fiora back in lane, healthy and ahead. Fiora goes all-in again. Dies. Does it again, and again, and again, and again.
